1. Student Date of Birth Not Displayed

Issue:
The student date of birth is not visible in the Student Profile View after the student is added.

Impact:
Admin and teachers cannot verify student age or personal details correctly.

To-Do / Fix:

Bind the date_of_birth field correctly from the database to the Student Profile UI.

Ensure the field is included in both view and API response layers.

2. Student Details Cannot Be Edited After Creation

Issue:
Once a student is added, student details cannot be edited.

Impact:
Admin cannot update incorrect or changed information.

To-Do / Fix:

Allow admin to edit all student details except the Student ID.

Fields allowed to update:

Name

Date of birth

Address

Parent contact details

Class assignment

Student ID must remain read-only to preserve data integrity.

3. Missing “None” Option in Class Filter

Issue:
The class filter does not have a “None / All Classes” option.

Impact:
Admin and teachers cannot easily view:

All students

Students without a class assignment

To-Do / Fix:

Add a “None” or “All” option to the class filter dropdown.

Default filter should show all students when no class is selected.

4. Admin Control Limitation

Issue:
Admin currently has limited control over modifying student records after creation.

Impact:
System flexibility is reduced in real-world usage.

To-Do / Fix:

Grant admin full edit permission for student records.

Maintain role-based access control so teachers and parents cannot modify restricted fields.

